{"lastModified":1767962986724,"uri":"c::22672890147::vessel::9c02b0b0-da56-11f0-838b-3500b00afa26","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: South Peloponnese, Navarino bay\n\nRock 36 embodies a stunning combination of energy and sophistication, highlighted by her smooth lines and curves.\n\nWith an aerodynamically designed console and comfortable helm station, a generous walk-around deck, two spacious lounging areas, and a cozy hidden cabin space beneath the front sunbed, this boat truly stands out. This blend of features, crafted in-house, focuses on enhancing the driver's experience by prioritizing functionality while ensuring optimal comfort for all passengers.\n\nThe attention to detail in her design and construction sets the Rock 36 apart, delivering an exceptional and enjoyable boating experience.\n\nExcellent Performance: Crafted to deliver an exceptional experience whether you're enjoying a leisurely cruise with friends or speeding over the waves, Rock 36's ability to ensure precise handling and comfort in any weather makes it a prime example of how high performance and ease of use can come together seamlessly.\n\nInnovative Hull: The custom-engineered hull of Rock 36 is specifically crafted to complement the boat's design. It features a ventilated triple-step structure that efficiently transforms engine power into speed, along with a 23º deadrise that guarantees an exceptionally stable and smooth ride.\n\nFunctional Console And User-Friendly Helm Station: Rock 36 is equipped with a driving console that features an aerodynamic hardtop and a stylish windshield, offering protection for the helm station from water and sunlight—perfectly suited for extended cruising adventures. The dual helm station is outfitted with spacious, shock-absorbing bucket seats covered in high-quality marine upholstery, along with advanced multi-display screens and various details that enhance comfort, creating an optimal experience for those at the helm. Positioned in front of the console is a comfortable seat that can optionally provide headroom underneath, complete with a sink and basin for added convenience.\n\nInviting Lounging Areas: Rock 36 offers a delightful experience for all guests, with two separate relaxation areas capable of accommodating up to 10 people. For the 36S edition, there is a large, delta-shaped sunbed and a console couch in the forward area, while at the aft there is a big sunbed paired with a back-to-back console couch.\n\nCabin Space: Underneath the delta bow sunbed, there is a comfortable bed designed for two. This area can be conveniently converted into waterproof storage.","blueprint":{"name":"AELIA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::9c02b0b0-da56-11f0-838b-3500b00afa26::assets::009c8e90-da59-11f0-bab1-49b810eaa29c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::9c02b0b0-da56-11f0-838b-3500b00afa26::assets::009b2f00-da59-11f0-bab1-49b810eaa29c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::9c02b0b0-da56-11f0-838b-3500b00afa26::assets::009b07f0-da59-11f0-bab1-49b810eaa29c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::9c02b0b0-da56-11f0-838b-3500b00afa26::assets::009f26a0-da59-11f0-bab1-49b810eaa29c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::9c02b0b0-da56-11f0-838b-3500b00afa26::assets::009e8a60-da59-11f0-bab1-49b810eaa29c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::9c02b0b0-da56-11f0-838b-3500b00afa26::assets::0099a860-da59-11f0-bab1-49b810eaa29c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::9c02b0b0-da56-11f0-838b-3500b00afa26::assets::009bf250-da59-11f0-bab1-49b810eaa29c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::9c02b0b0-da56-11f0-838b-3500b00afa26::assets::009a92c0-da59-11f0-bab1-49b810eaa29c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::9c02b0b0-da56-11f0-838b-3500b00afa26::assets::009c4070-da59-11f0-bab1-49b810eaa29c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::9c02b0b0-da56-11f0-838b-3500b00afa26::assets::009e3c40-da59-11f0-bab1-49b810eaa29c/{imageVariant}